WEBVTT

57:27.108 --> 57:29.358
Using that phone's IMEI number,
we found something.

57:29.816 --> 57:32.441
Until about a year ago, another number
was used on that phone.

57:32.483 --> 57:33.816
That number is still active.

57:33.858 --> 57:35.899
But it's now linked
to a different IMEI number.

57:36.649 --> 57:38.983
Which means he must
have sold the phone.
